            "name": "Monster Core pg. 231",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Monster Core",
          "page": 231,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Merfolk wavecallers use their primal magic to defend their people. Their ability to asphyxiate airbreathers makes them crucial when surface dwellers invade.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
