                "name": "Player Core pg. 457",
                "type": "link"
              },
              "name": "Player Core",
              "page": 457,
              "type": "source"
            }
          ],
          "text": "Humanoid creatures reason and act much like humans. They typically stand upright and have two arms and two legs.",
          "type": "trait"
        },
